一人一個profile方便監控咋<br />\n而家立法會收埋皮，過多一排過埋23條就含撚都無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57664a813fa71402184c8e23dd5e8f7f0bb9d24","tid":499773,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"BTW 政府班官係咪以為移動支付得qr code,唔知有nfc?"},{"pid":"3008829ead031324917b791e082e7cac404da771","tid":499773,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW 政府班官係咪以為移動支付得qr code,唔知有nfc?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日後順理成章俾支那寶玩哂"},{"pid":"c1e06a75d3c30513eb3463658e6116cb3bc31d55","tid":499773,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e3d51147923cde47fe8a6cce2f7bc81439b2b8a","tid":499773,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BTW 政府班官係咪以為移動支付得qr code,唔知有nfc?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日後順理成章俾支那寶玩哂</blockquote><br />\n上次先同genzo兄講足幾版<br />\nHKMA牽頭只可以搞個software side既qr code俾唔同既payment app去跟<br />\nnfc部部機唔同standard唔同type<br />\n一d有呢隻冇個隻，一d鎖起唔俾你用，一d直情冇<br />\n連八仔同蘋果合作d咁既野就已經做唔到<br />\n唔好話你要蘋果三星華為sony小米htc齊齊聽你話開隻特別for香港既版本<br />\n諗都諗到冇可能<br />\n揀qr code係合理</blockquote><br />\nmobile suica 又有samsung LG htc Sony aquos<br />\n<br />\nsupport NFC type F 加 security chipset/HCE硬件上功能已經齊，差左software肯唔肯放權<br />\n<br />\nNFC為主幹QR為輔咪ok,NFC 快速支付(交通卡)用，QR就俾d裝唔到NFC的地方用"},{"pid":"3a8665c6acff2c4c550873c622530c6f3acf3487","tid":499773,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"咁多年都唔搞匯豐銀通聯網<br />\n信佢會做到野?"}]}